original_title: The Royal Wedding: HRH Prince William & Catherine Middleton
overview: Join HRH Prince William and Catherine Middleton at Westminster Abbey as they celebrate the momentous occasion of their marriage. Footage includes Catherine's breathtaking arrival at  Westminster Abbey, the full ceremony, the carriage procession and the traditional balcony appearance at Buckingham Palace.  Presented by Huw Edwards
